<li><span class="languageicon" style="font-size:0.95em; font-weight:bold; color:#555;">(Hungarian)</span> <span id="CITEREFVeszpr.C3.A9my1994" class="citation book">Veszprémy, László (1994). "Gizella". In Kristó, Gyula; Engel, Pál; Makk, Ferenc. <i>Korai magyar történeti lexikon (9–14. század)</i> [Encyclopedia of the Early Hungarian History (9th–14th centuries)]. Akadémiai Kiadó. pp.&#160;236–237. <a href="/wiki/International_Standard_Book_Number" title="International Standard Book Number">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/963-05-6722-9" title="Special:BookSources/963-05-6722-9">963-05-6722-9</a>.</span><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AStephen+I+of+Hungary&amp;rft.atitle=Gizella&amp;rft.aufirst=L%C3%A1szl%C3%B3&amp;rft.aulast=Veszpr%C3%A9my&amp;rft.au=Veszpr%C3%A9my%2C+L%C3%A1szl%C3%B3&amp;rft.btitle=Korai+magyar+t%C3%B6rt%C3%A9neti+lexikon+%289%E2%80%9314.+sz%C3%A1zad%29+%5BEncyclopedia+of+the+Early+Hungarian+History+%289th%E2%80%9314th+centuries%29%5D&amp;rft.date=1994&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.isbn=963-05-6722-9&amp;rft.pages=236-237&amp;rft.pub=Akad%C3%A9miai+Kiad%C3%B3&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook" class="Z3988"><span style="display:none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
